defaultIn setting this framework, I have aimed to 
defaultfoster an intelligent approach to performance management whereby:
default&#xa0;
default1.1.3
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThe terminology contained within my plan is important as it reflects my desire to move away from a primarily target-driven culture in favour of a more balanced approach that considers the wider objectives and the behaviours they drive. I have not, for exam
defaultple used the term ‘target’ in my Police and Crime Plan, but instead made reference to ‘indicators’ and ‘ambitions’.
default&#xa0;
default 
default&#xa0;
default1.1.4
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultI do not believe that the nine Police and Crime measures alone can tell us whether we are achieving the aspirations of the plan, but I do
default recognise their importance in helping us to understand and communicate progress against a complex area of business to a wide variety of audiences. I also feel that there is a public and organisational desire for clear tangible outcomes against my overall 
defaultambition which I have aimed to balance proportionately within my Police and Crime Plan.
default&#xa0;
default1.2. default&#xa0;default&#xa0;default&#xa0;default&#xa0;default&#xa0;default&#xa0;default&#xa0;default&#xa0;default&#xa0;default&#xa0;default What impact do you think these targets have on police recording crime practices?default&#xa0;
default1.2.1
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultOf the nine ambitions set as part of my Police and Crime Plan, four r
defaultely upon police recorded crime data.
default&#xa0;
default I have engaged with officers and staff at a various levels of the organisation to develop an understanding of the impact of my priorities and the small number of numerical indicators that support them.
default&#xa0;
default This will culmi
defaultnate in a meeting with performance and priority leads in January ahead of the annual refresh of my Police and Crime Plan.
default&#xa0;
default 
default1.2.2
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultIn addition to this oversight, the Constabulary has reviewed attitudes, perceptions and behaviours with regard to performance cultu
defaultre through its performance review process as part of a programme of work to drive improvements in crime recording standards.
default&#xa0;
default Active oversight of this work has helped to inform my view.
default&#xa0;
default1.2.3
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultI have concluded that there is evidence to suggest that a historic or
defaultganisational target-driven culture has, at times, led to pressure on staff to behave in a way that 
defaultputs performance ahead of the victim when recording crime.
default&#xa0;
default This was supported by a recent internal poll of officers and staff in Avon and Somerset.
default&#xa0;
default1.2.4
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultI feel 
defaultconfident, however, that the organisation has undergone a significant cultural shift over recent years, which has resulted in a more analytical and less target-driven approach to driving performance improvement. While this is clearly evident at senior leve
defaultls within the organisation, I share a desire to ensure that this is effectively communicated and fully recognised at all levels within the organisation.
default&#xa0;
default1.2.5
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultI believe that the safeguards to ensuring an accurate, ethical and reliable approach to crime recordin
defaultg lie in the organisation’s approach to 
defaultperformance culturedefault more generally as opposed to the concept of measurable aspirations as part of the Police and Crime Plan.
default&#xa0;
default I do however recognise that I have a role to play in shaping this culture both through the
default plan and in my interactions with officers and staff, and will continue to review my approach in light of new and emerging findings.
default&#xa0;
default1.2.6
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThere are, however, a number of areas where my 
defaultstrategic prioritiesdefault have had a direct impact upon crime recording practice
defaults.
default&#xa0;
default In 2013, for example, the Constabulary introduced a flag for commercial burglary which enabled the organisation to improve analysis and interventions in response to my burglary reduction priority.
default&#xa0;
default Similarly, a focus on improving crime recording standa
defaultrds with regard to domestic violence resulted in earlier and more accurate identification of domestic violence victims.
default&#xa0;
default While this has not been driven by an increase in victim reporting it is clearly a positive outcome in enabling greater identification, 
defaultsupport and safeguarding amongst victims of these crimes.
default&#xa0;
default2.1default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultHow do you assure yourself that the recorded crime figures for your area are correct?default&#xa0;default2.1.1default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultI actively seek assurance with regard to the accuracy of crime data through a variety of mechanisms and recognise that our intelligence, analysis, operational effectiveness and service provision are all dependent upon the information we record and process.
default&#xa0;
default 
default&#xa0;default2.1.2default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThere has been a dedicated programme of work in Avon and Somerset to improve crime recording standards prompted by HMIC Crime and Incident Recording Inspections and key findings from HMIC’s work in Kent in February 2013. This led to a Gold and Silver G
defaultroup being established and I am represented on both.
default&#xa0;
default As part of this process, I maintain ongoing oversight of crime recording compliance and progress against a dedicated improvement plan.
default&#xa0;
default2.1.3default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultI also directly oversee issues relating to crime recording and dat
defaulta integrity through my regular 1:1 meetings with respective Chief Officer Portfolio holders for crime recording and performance. 
default&#xa0;
default2.1.4default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultWhile these internal oversight arrangements provide some level of assurance, I also place great value on external and indepen
defaultdent sources of assurance, including the HMIC inspection which offers broader comparisons against other police forces nationally.
default&#xa0;default2.2.1default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultTo what extent can you trust the crime statistics for your area? default&#xa0;default2.2.2default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultMy trust in the recorded crime statistics for Avon and Som
defaulterset is borne out of a realistic understanding of the limitations of this data and what the crime statistics represent.
default&#xa0;
default I understand, for example, that they can only ever be a reflection of what is reported to or pro-actively identified by the police, an
defaultd for a variety of reasons, would not rely on police recorded crime statistics to give an indication of overall levels or trends in crime.
default&#xa0;
default 
default&#xa0;
default2.2.3
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultIn my view, the important question is whether we and our partner organisations can trust the recorded crime data t
defaulto accurately identify the nature of victimisation, risk and vulnerability.
default&#xa0;
default This is critical to ensuring appropriate and effective victim focussed service responses and safeguarding our most vulnerable people from harm.
default&#xa0;
default While I understand that volume crim
defaulte data is always likely to contain some margin of error, I believe that further work can still be done to mitigate these risks. 
default&#xa0;
default2.2.4
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultI recognise that Avon and Somerset has been consistently identified as having one of the lowest levels of compliance nationall
defaulty across areas such as incident to crime conversion - while also having one of the highest rates of no crime decisions.
default&#xa0;
default These 
defaultfindings are a source of shared concern, however, I am now confident that the Constabulary is working hard to drive sustained imp
defaultrovements in the accuracy of the data they record and retain.
default&#xa0;
default 
default&#xa0;
