defaultI have been particularly encouraged by the Constabulary’s approach in seeking to understand the drivers of poor quality recording and tailor their solutions accordingly – be they training, system and process improvement, supervision and leadership, culture
default or capacity.
default&#xa0;
default Recent developments have included:- 
